org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.process.traversal.step

Interface FromToModulating

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AddEdgeStep, PathFilterStep, PathStep

    public interface FromToModulating
    FromToModulating are for Steps that support from()- and to()-modulation. This step is similar to ByModulating.
    Author:
    Marko A. Rodriguez (http://markorodriguez.com)
